items.name: Elsa & Fred
items.text: This is the story of two people who, at the end of the road, discover that it's never too late to love. After losing his wife, Fred feels disturbed, confused and alone, so his daughter helps move him into a nearby apartment building where he meets Elsa. From that moment on, everything changes. Elsa bursts into Fred's life like a whirlwind, determined to teach him that time is precious and that he should enjoy life-and love-to the fullest.
